{"tid":570584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰紐約返港又延誤4個鐘  轉機客行程受阻","createTime":"2018-02-23T19:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T01:00:03.000Z","uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8e157bdbb18afbfca8e098578f19ae0a1e3d59","tid":570584,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T19:00:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因管理不善而在全球最佳航空公司排名節節下跌的國泰航空</span>又出現航班延誤，打亂不少轉機乘客的計劃。有港人原定於美國時間周四(22日)早上9時乘搭國泰CX841航班，由紐約甘迺迪國際機場返港，但抵達當地機場時，才得知航班要延誤4小時，不少乘客逼爆當地櫃枱，有乘客擔心抵港後未能趕及轉機，行程受阻。 <br />\n<br />\n國泰發言人表示，由於航機調動關係，國泰航空一班原定於美國時間周四早上9時，由紐約甘迺迪返港的CX841航班，需要順延至同日當地時間下午1時12分才能啟程。公司已為乘客提供膳食，亦為轉機乘客重新安排接駁航班或改乘其他航空公司之航班，就事件對乘客帶來不便再次致歉。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/025854_8427901f888180b43a5e676620be98b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F025854_8427901f888180b43a5e676620be98b8.png&h=1eeb72d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰紐約飛香港的航機延誤，大批乘客在登機閘口乾着急。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180223/mobile/bkn-20180223213319444-0223_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402883474e2f2b2f014e3deb1e7f4fac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180223%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180223213319444-0223_00822_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_news%26eventID%3D402883474e2f2b2f014e3deb1e7f4fac&d=T0kcINzu%2BlKuzfwfImsmTwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c98b331e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180223/mobile/bkn-20180223213319444-0223_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402883474e2f2b2f014e3deb1e7f4fac</a>"},{"pid":"cc02d753b80c9f78e9baba198e37e4d57d8e4d17","tid":570584,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"入黎就係為左睇依句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94605364dc1d2c9d4bf6d4395b5f57b4fe4a2ebf","tid":570584,"uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T19:42:47.000Z","msg":"幅圖明明係America Airline"},{"pid":"e53935288c74bf5f923037bc6fac28fd5cacdae2","tid":570584,"uid":33213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T20:12:56.000Z","msg":"delay都上報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e19de1a2909796915dc7f8a3290e3df66171fa1","tid":570584,"uid":68285,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T21:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個旅客真係醒 識搵東方"},{"pid":"88f141ebd652cb156658fb2ae9c2ba77d7f183ec","tid":570584,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:00:03.000Z","msg":"日日都有飛機delayed"}]}